These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, drama, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person watching documentary movies##2
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching drama movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching animation movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel         | documentary   | drama | animation       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
City: boston, prague, london, paris
1. the person traveling to paris is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person traveling to prague##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| City   | prague    | paris   | boston | london       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, skateboard, tram, van
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the colombian is between the british and the person driving the skateboard##2
3. the british is on the far left##1
4. the french is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Transport          | van    | airplane | skateboard   | tram  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, australian, polish, nigerian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, rugby, tennis
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is the australian##1
2. the mexican is between the person who's sport is basketball and the nigerian##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
4. the mexican is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality     | nigerian   | mexican    | polish       | australian   |
| Sport   | rugby | tennis | basketball | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, jazz, d&b
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, dancing, magic-tricks, skydiving
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is dancing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Music-Genre   | disco        | jazz | d&b  | hip-hop |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | dancing  | skydiving | card-games    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, subway, jet-ski
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rowing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Transport   | helicopter     | subway           | airplane | jet-ski  |
| Sport         | cycling | skateboarding | parkour   | rowing |

