.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, house, punk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower, poppy, dahlia
1. the fan of gospel is the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the fan of electronic is between the person who growsdaisy and the fan of house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | gospel | electronic | house      |
| Flower     | poppy | daisy    | bellflower  | dahlia |

