.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, weightlifting
City: boston, miami, venice, liverpool
1. the person traveling to boston is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person traveling to miami is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person traveling to venice##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| City   | venice   | miami     | liverpool | boston |

