.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
House: victorian, colonial, gothic-revival, cape-cod
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the colonial house##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the colonial house and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| House    | cape-cod   | gothic-revival      | colonial   | victorian  |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |

