.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
4 different games are played: go, scrabble, bridge, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, sports
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing chess is between the person watching sports movies and the person playing go##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the person playing go is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Game           | go | chess | scrabble | bridge     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary    | sports   | adventure |

