.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-14::.
4 different games are played: snooker, go, monopoly, scrabble
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, martial-arts, spy
1. the person playing go is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching epic movies##2
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Game           | snooker | scrabble | monopoly | go |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | animation | spy         | martial-arts |

