.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, fonseca, bluemaster, havana
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, family, mystery
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the havana-smoker is between the person watching mystery movies and the swisher-smoker##2
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Cigar         | swisher      | havana | fonseca  | bluemaster |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family  | mystery | adventure    |

