.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, french, japanese
4 different games are played: backgammon, poker, monopoly, go
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the japanese is the person playing monopoly##1
3. the french is between the person playing monopoly and the dutch##2
4. the japanese is on the right of the french##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | dutch | french | japanese |
| Game     | backgammon     | poker   | go | monopoly  |

