.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, february, july, september
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, lizard, rabbit
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the person who's birthday is in february##2
4. the owner of the rabbit is the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | september | february | april | july |
| Pet           | lizard  | rabbit  | goldfish | goat      |

