.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, milk, lemonade
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person drinking cola and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking cola##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Beverage   | cola    | juice  | lemonade    | milk       |

