2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the polish is the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person traveling to paris is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| City         | new-york | marseilles | paris     | hannover    |

